Instance nat_naturals_to_semiring : NaturalsToSemiRing@{N i} nat :=
  fun _ _ _ _ _ _ => fix f (n: nat) := match n with 0%nat => 0 | 1%nat => 1 |
   S n' => 1 + f n' end.
